{"tid":1986771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工賊會無良炒人，又賣工人，事主要搵泛民議員求助","createTime":"2020-04-24T05:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T13:42:48.000Z","uid":221035,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb280876fed96c73891316889b95f9f9d3f8a8b","tid":1986771,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:09:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E4%B8%8B%E9%81%AD%E5%B7%A5%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E5%B1%AC%E6%9C%83%E8%A7%A3%E5%83%B1-%E9%BB%83%E5%A5%B3%E5%A3%AB-%E4%BD%9C%E7%82%BA%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94-%E9%BB%9E%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%92%81%E6%B6%BC%E8%96%84/?fbclid=IwAR1MIVyJnSegyV9oJd_ZQTICc0xAZvuV84i6TryuIM72GLDCa4iMU7N3eao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%2583%25B1-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25A3%25AB-%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%258B%259E%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594-%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%2592%2581%25E6%25B6%25BC%25E8%2596%2584%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1MIVyJnSegyV9oJd_ZQTICc0xAZvuV84i6TryuIM72GLDCa4iMU7N3eao&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hVSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=bc28821c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%2583%25B1-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25A3%25AB-%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%258B%259E%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594-%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%2592%2581%25E6%25B6%25BC%25E8%2596%2584%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1MIVyJnSegyV9oJd_ZQTICc0xAZvuV84i6TryuIM72GLDCa4iMU7N3eao&h=51e98355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E4%B8%8B%E9%81%AD%E5%B7%A5%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E5%B1%AC%E6%9C%83%E8%A7%A3%E5%83%B1-%E9%BB%83%E5%A5%B3%E5%A3%AB-%E4%BD%9C%E7%82%BA%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94-%E9%BB%9E%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%92%81%E6%B6%BC%E8%96%84/?fbclid=IwAR1MIVyJnSegyV9oJd_ZQTICc0xAZvuV84i6TryuIM72GLDCa4iMU7N3eao</a><br />\n<br />\n//黃女士今年五十出頭，入職工聯會屬會&mdash;香港洋務工會逾 6 年。她本來是一名會務員，自認工作認真負責、誠誠懇懇，和同事關係良好，從沒收過投訴或警告。怎知上月 31 日突然收到解僱通知，令她十分愕然和不解。<br />\n<br />\n黃女士以為自己屬借調性質，根據過往經驗，可回到總部工作。然而，她在翌日被告知自己同樣「被炒」，她遂向工會秘書長湯女士和副主席邱先生查詢解僱理由，對方僅稱是「工會整體安排」，又指已無合適職位、工會經濟困難等，湯更向她說，「你適應下啦！」<br />\n<br />\n黃女士認為，對方的言論十分涼薄，「我畀人炒喎，叫我適應？作為勞工團體，點可以講出咁涼薄的說話？」她認為工會並非經濟困難，上月初更增聘一名全職、一名兼職會務員，更與她年紀相若。她感到不忿和諷刺，自己年年跟工會出席五一遊行，「你（工聯會）唔係應該有社會責任㗎咩？每一個五一高舉旗幟，話要撐勞工、爭福利，到頭來點解可以咁無情對一個小職員？」黃女士亦兩度嘗試聯絡工聯會求助，對方均指會了解情況，就再無音信。//<br />\n<br />\n黃女士最後去咗搵林卓廷幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d0f0f6df1f6df09f06e522b824930071e4d60d","tid":1986771,"uid":221035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:10:10.000Z","msg":"快啲share俾啲藍絲親戚"},{"pid":"014c6b76f5b7f2fd450143721b8d4715df55943b","tid":1986771,"uid":221035,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:10:36.000Z","msg":"口說撐勞工反攬炒嘅工聯會，出賣工人最快手"},{"pid":"ec518458296a65845193beb726b8183263df9c4e","tid":1986771,"uid":161374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:11:59.000Z","msg":"工會都無錢，睇黎中共科水都科唔到"},{"pid":"3450363517424c109b3e86d2fcd91466e3ae9d92","tid":1986771,"uid":31542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:13:27.000Z","msg":"叫佢搵吳秋北啦"},{"pid":"20f58f2572d5f27ad00121f686f2d6c8123c7f57","tid":1986771,"uid":245033,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:13:29.000Z","msg":"好耐之前咪係有句咩工聯會出賣工人之類嘅金句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fce23262e4b82d49f58776f124b85f5fb8a1633","tid":1986771,"uid":9049,"