"tid":1986771,"uid":168567,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:48:41.000Z","msg":"所以藍絲只會對影響自己利益既事關心奉行利己主義<br />\n你見中共港共出既文宣<br />\n都係打 &quot;你影響經濟&quot; &quot;你影響派錢&quot; &quot;你影響民生&quot;<br />\n有一期我地既文宣係打&quot;你支持政府 = 損害自己既利益&quot;<br />\n可惜發生得太多野 同埋俾人令到個重點濛糊左 SPIN走左<br />\n你同佢地講警暴幾嚴重  佢地唔會有感覺<br />\n所以我地文宣要加強針對 中共點樣益自己人 而無視市民利益<br />\n一國兩制被廢 香港變成中國城市後 市民利益會點樣受損 等等"},{"pid":"7afe7cdee516f1d535c9d2ae44009b7cb3ef20d4","tid":1986771,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bcbda553dd1a4ae003f70056641c5e5e6e7961","tid":1986771,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:13:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0b3baccb0e8002029635dc8c2cab9e5b18ba0cb8","tid":1986771,"uid":182061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:27:12.000Z","msg":"工賊會幾時都企喺打工仔對面㗎啦"},{"pid":"3b4970936ca597bdb7ec075e8cec3aa800519425","tid":1986771,"uid":203397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:36:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9424ad7e63ef06200bea63943af392b2a5037dd","tid":1986771,"uid":180429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:37:23.000Z","msg":"之前潘曉穎老豆老母都係搵民建聯架嘛<br />\n後果係點大家有眼見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係今時今日先知道班奶共派咩為人下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a467f855454a83224907355efae422243d95baef","tid":1986771,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:47:48.000Z","msg":"鄧家彪、王國興、黃國健、吳秋北去咗邊<br />\n日日玩政治，唔理工人死活<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fb163bf6f16fe7435b3b53febe056ba8a55c30","tid":1986771,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:53:17.000Z","msg":"炒外人比佢地自己人入去姐"},{"pid":"06d22158d521edf4f41a52920eb23ec61073ec0f","tid":1986771,"uid":57634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"20f58f2572d5f27ad00121f686f2d6c8123c7f57","tid":1986771,"uid":245033,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:13:29.000Z","msg":"好耐之前咪係有句咩工聯會出賣工人之類嘅金句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T06:54:48.000Z","msg":"今次《施政報告》在取消強積金對沖機制上「走數」，在立法會擁有6票的工聯會，在「致謝議案」的投票立場一直備受關注，最終3位工聯會議員立法會議員黃國健、王國興和郭偉強均投下支持票，向梁振英「致謝」。另外3位議員包括陳婉嫻、麥美娟、鄧家彪則缺席。工聯會最終有3票支持這份被視為向打工仔「走數」的施政報告，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃國健代工聯會解畫時，一度說錯「我哋幾時都係企喺打工仔嘅對面」</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20160219/54777631\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160219%2F54777631&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hVSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=d62ea45e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160219%2F54777631&h=b864ec9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20160219/54777631</a>"},{"pid":"ab7258b032f57ae2c44ed234719ea0ea436c7024","tid":1986771,"uid":57634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T07:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/